<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08051i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08051i">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08051i"> 51(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> they thought they were in / Mary&apos;s month when / lo came snow </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: According to the legend of the founding of the Church of St Mary of Snow, on the Esquiline Hill in Rome, Mary appeared in a dream to a wealthy Roman, John, and to Pope Liberius, saying that she wished to have a new church dedicated to her and that the site would be marked by snow. Snow fell the next day, even though it was August, a month also marked (on the 15th) by the Feast of Mary&apos;s Assumption into heaven. <font color="green">[Vincent Deane.]</font> </mm> </dd></dl>
